Manual Batch Reply System
Overview 
Captures client messages 24/7
Extracts URLs from Instagram, LinkedIn, Twitter, Facebook (new share format), and article sites
Saves message description (what you/client writes)
Stores all metadata (Chat ID, Message ID, timestamps)
You add replies in bulk (10, 20, 50+ at once)
Click button in Google Sheet
All pending replies sent simultaneously
Threaded to original messages
Status updates to "Sent" automatically


