## üìß Project 1: Email Automation System

### Overview
Automated daily email distribution with 1-3 dynamic attachments, reducing manual work from 15 minutes to 2 minutes per execution.

### Workflow Diagram
![Email Workflow](screenshots/email-automation/workflow-overview.png)

### Key Features
- ‚úÖ Dynamic template selection (1, 2, or 3 files)
- ‚úÖ Google Sheets integration
- ‚úÖ Gmail API automation
- ‚úÖ BCC support
- ‚úÖ Daily scheduling

### Sample Output
![Email Received](screenshots/email-automation/email-received.png)

### Technical Stack
- **Platform:** n8n
- **APIs:** Google Sheets, Gmail
- **Nodes Used:** Schedule, Read Sheets, Merge, Send Email
- **Execution Time:** ~10 seconds

