- ‚úÖ **Pareto Analysis** - 80/20 rule calculations
- ‚úÖ **Anomaly Detection** - Z-score based outlier identification
- ‚úÖ **Performance Segmentation** - High/Medium/Low categorization
- ‚úÖ **Concentration Risk** - Market share analysis
- ‚úÖ **Strategic Recommendations** - Data-driven action items

### Statistical Methods Used
- Mean, Standard Deviation
- Coefficient of Variation
- Z-Score Analysis (2-sigma threshold)
- Pareto Principle
