## üõ†Ô∏è Installation & Setup

### Prerequisites
```
- n8n (cloud or self-hosted)
- Google Sheets API credentials
- Gmail/Telegram API credentials
- API2PDF API key
```

### Quick Start
1. Import JSON workflow to n8n
2. Configure API credentials
3. Update Google Sheet IDs in nodes
4. Test execution manually
5. Enable schedule trigger

### Configuration Tips
- Schedule: Modify cron expression in Schedule Trigger node
- Recipients: Update in Google Sheets (no code changes needed!)
- Chart sizes: Change width/height in HTTP Request URLs
- PDF format: Adjust HTML/CSS in Code nodes

